3. THIRD-PARTY DATA
==========================================================================

data/quran/qac_morphology.txt is the Quranic Arabic Corpus (morphology
version 0.4) by Kais Dukes (University of Leeds, 2011), distributed under
the GNU General Public License (GPL). The full copyright block is preserved
at the top of the file. This redistribution does not modify the data.

data/quran/quran_check.json contains the Tanzil Quran text (Uthmani
edition), distributed under Creative Commons Attribution–NoDerivatives 3.0
Unported (CC-BY-ND 3.0).

When you use either dataset, please cite the upstream sources directly:
- Dukes, Kais. (2011). Quranic Arabic Corpus. https://corpus.quran.com
- Tanzil Project. https://tanzil.net
